hardn-xdr (2.0.0-1) stable; urgency=medium

  * Packaged release of HARDN-XDR - Linux Security Hardening Sentinel.
  * Includes automated installation of major security packages.
  * Sets up kernel and user-space hardening rules.
  * Provides STIG-compliant base configuration.
  * Ships with user-friendly `hardn-xdr` launcher and modular scripts.

